\begin_inset Formula $\|S^{-1}\delta_{s}\|_{2}\leq\frac{\epsilon}{1-\epsilon}$
\end_inset

.
 Therefore, when 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon<\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

